cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with speech recognition in multiple languages and proposes a universal character set for all languages. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also likely as the paper deals with speech recognition. 
- cs.LG (Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a language-specific gating mechanism within the network. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with end-to-end speech recognition. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper proposes a system for multilingual speech recognition.
